    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/speedy-caprese-glorious-grain-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s] </strong>in half lengthways, around the stone</p><p>Remove the<strong> stone[s]</strong> using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh </strong>and slice finely lengthways</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/speedy-caprese-glorious-grain-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into large bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/speedy-caprese-glorious-grain-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> in half</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/speedy-caprese-glorious-grain-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Squeeze your pouch[es] of <strong>glorious grains</strong> to separate the grains</p><p>Tear the top corner of the pouch[es] (just a little!) and <strong>microwave</strong> for 2 min or until piping hot</p><p>Tip: If you're cooking two or more pouches, pop them in together but increase the microwave cook time accordingly</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/speedy-caprese-glorious-grain-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/speedy-caprese-glorious-grain-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>traditional Italian pesto </strong>in a bowl with your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>pesto salad dressing</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/speedy-caprese-glorious-grain-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spinach</strong> in the base of the bowl and top with the <strong>warmed grains</strong>, <strong>chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>sliced avocado</strong> and <strong>halved mozzarella</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>pesto salad dressing </strong>and garnish with your <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
